API -.->|status=executed/expired| DB

PWA -->|Access Request Form| API
API -->|create request\nemail token| DB
API -->|DOI Mail| PWA
PWA -->|Confirm Token| API
API -->|assign groups| DB

DEVICE -.->|No inbound connections\nPull only| API
